Subject: [PATCH] add NumPy 2.5 support

Backport the compatibility changes from upstream Numba PR #10645
(commit f16e5c9dda74812789c9cdd6aa8416d04fe1f164). The upstream PR is
not merged yet; this local package intentionally tests that work against
the repository's NumPy 2.5 package.

